<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c3">{وَأَقِمِ الصَّلَاةَ طَرَفَيِ النَّهَارِ وَزُلَفًا مِنَ اللَّيْلِ، إِنَّ الحَسَنَاتِ يُذْهِبْنَ السَّيِّئَاتِ , ذَلِكَ ذِكْرَى لِلذَّاكِرِينَ}</span> <span class="c2">(١)</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c5">قَالَ الْبُخَارِيُّ ج٦ص٧٥:</span> <span class="c3">{وَزُلَفًا}</span>: سَاعَاتٍ بَعْدَ سَاعَاتٍ،<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>وَمِنْهُ سُمِّيَتِ المُزْدَلِفَةُ،<span class="c5"> الزُّلَفُ:</span> مَنْزِلَةٌ بَعْدَ مَنْزِلَةٍ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>وَأَمَّا <span class="c3">{زُلْفَى}</span> <span class="c2">(٢)</span>: فَمَصْدَرٌ مِنَ القُرْبَى،<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c5">ازْدَلَفُوا:</span> اجْتَمَعُوا.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c3">{أَزْلَفْنَا}</span> <span class="c2">(٣)</span>: جَمَعْنَا.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<hr>
<p class="hamesh">(١) [هود: ١١٤]<br>(٢) [سبأ: ٣٧]<br>(٣) [الشعراء: ٦٤]</p> </div>